title: dallas 11x07 Last Tango in Dallas.avi
description:
YES boys and girls, it is finally here:
DALLAS season 11 brings you another 30 great episodes of the Ewing saga.


Bobby and Christopher take a liking to Lisa Alden, while Jenna and Ray grow closer; Clayton's heart is still a source of concern for Miss Ellie; J.R. gets dirt on Weststar and meets Nicholas Pearce; Cliff tries to appease Dandy Dandridge.

original air date : Friday October 30, 1987

The episode title is a play on the movie, Last Tango in Paris.
